# Redirect rules for the Jujube rebrand (old domain -> new domain).
# NOTE: GitHub Pages does NOT honor this file. It is provided for when the
# old domain (fridgenie.app) is served via Netlify or Cloudflare Pages, which
# DO honor _redirects. See REBRAND_NOTES.md for the GitHub Pages path.
https://fridgenie.app/*   https://getjujube.app/:splat   301!
http://fridgenie.app/*    https://getjujube.app/:splat   301!
https://www.fridgenie.app/*  https://getjujube.app/:splat  301!
